            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 md:justify-start">
              <a href="#base-diet" class="font-sora rounded-full bg-clay px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-clay-dk">Start With the Base Diet →</a>
