        { stat: "60–80%", label: "Pellet Base", body: "Formulated pellets are the nutritional foundation — never an all-seed diet, which causes vitamin-A deficiency and a shorter life." },
        { stat: "15–20%", label: "Fresh Veg", body: "Dark leafy greens plus orange veg (sweet potato, carrot, red pepper) supply the vitamin A and calcium a Grey needs most." },
